Banca Nazionale del Lavoro ( London branch ) issuing 120 mln dlr , five-year straight bond equity warrant , lead manager Credit Suisse First Boston Ltd said .
The issue , matures April 3 , 1992 , indicated coupon 5-1/2 six pct par pricing .
Fees total 2-1/4 pct listing Luxembourg .
Payment date April 2 .
The bond sold denomination 1,000 dlrs one warrant attached , exercisable April 15 , 1987 April 3 , 1992 .
Each warrant entitle holder purchase 45 saving share EFI Banca premium 10 pct closing price Milan Stock Exchange March 17 .
EFI medium-term credit institution , 36-1/2 pct owned Banca Nazionale del Lavoro .
